                     <interp inst="t18440408-1304-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 3 shillings, 5 sixpences, and 1 groat; the monies of <persName id="t18440408-name-1493" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-1493" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
