                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-1495" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MARCHING</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 379.) I took the prisoner—I found nothing on him but a knife.</p>
